{"title":"Migration of Hexo+Github Pages","date":"2020-03-10T07:30:11.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 10, 2020","L":"03/10/2020","MM-DD":"03-10"},"link":"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages","comments":true,"tags":["website"],"updated":"2020-03-10T07:30:11.000Z","content":"<p>Due to the novel coronavirus epidemic situation, I can’t go back to the laboratory  to update my website. Fortunately, I backed up the website data. I want to update the website through my pc.</p>\n<p>Here are my implementation steps. (I will not repeat section 1 and 2, <a href=\"https://thswind.github.io/2020/01/14/hexo%2Bgithub%20pages%20deploy\" target=\"_blank\">https://thswind.github.io/2020/01/14/hexo%2Bgithub pages deploy</a>)</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-install-node.js\">1 Install node.js<a title=\"#1-install-node.js\" href=\"#1-install-node.js\"></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"2-install-git\">2 Install Git<a title=\"#2-install-git\" href=\"#2-install-git\"></a></h2>\n<h2 id=\"3-install-hexo\">3 Install hexo<a title=\"#3-install-hexo\" href=\"#3-install-hexo\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Open cmd console, switch to :</p>\n<p>​\tF:\\mywebsite\\blog</p>\n<p>And input this command, as below:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">F:\\<span class=\"title\">mywebsite</span>\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">npm</span> <span class=\"title\">install</span> <span class=\"title\">hexo</span>-<span class=\"title\">cli</span> -<span class=\"title\">g</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>initial your blog:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">F:\\<span class=\"title\">mywebsite</span>\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">hexo</span> <span class=\"title\">init</span> <span class=\"title\">thswind</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Warning: If your are failed, probably because of your internet speed is not good.</p>\n<p>Switch to thswind, and install some dependencies：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">F:\\<span class=\"title\">mywebsite</span>\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>\\<span class=\"title\">thswind</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">npm</span> <span class=\"title\">install</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Install a deployer:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">F:\\<span class=\"title\">mywebsite</span>\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>\\<span class=\"title\">thswind</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">npm</span> <span class=\"title\">install</span> <span class=\"title\">hexo</span>-<span class=\"title\">deployer</span>-<span class=\"title\">git</span> --<span class=\"title\">save</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"4-migration\">4 Migration<a title=\"#4-migration\" href=\"#4-migration\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>copy package.json package-lock.json from old pc to new pc</li>\n<li>copy thswind/source from old pc to thswind/source to new pc</li>\n<li>copy scaffolds to new pc</li>\n<li>copy themes to new pc</li>\n<li>copy blog\\thswind\\_config.yml to new pc</li>\n<li>copy thswind\\node_modules to new pc</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"problems\">Problems<a title=\"#problems\" href=\"#problems\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>After you finished  these steps, some error may occur because of China’s complex internet environment. How to deal with it? just follow me.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>ERROR Plugin load failed: hexo-renderer-scss</p>\n<p>To solve this problem, you can through this command:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">F:\\<span class=\"title\">mywebsite</span>\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>\\<span class=\"title\">thswind</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">npm</span> <span class=\"title\">install</span> <span class=\"title\">hexo</span>-<span class=\"title\">renderer</span>-<span class=\"title\">scss</span> --<span class=\"title\">save</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>If failed again, it means you can’t visit <a href=\"http://www.github.com\">www.github.com</a> normally. You can visit it indirectly through ‘mirror’ website. <a href=\"http://www.gitee.com/mirrors\">www.gitee.com/mirrors</a> is a good choice.</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cmd\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"> F:\\<span class=\"title\">mywebsite</span>\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>\\<span class=\"title\">thswind</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">npm</span> <span class=\"title\">install</span> -<span class=\"title\">g</span> <span class=\"title\">mirror</span>-<span class=\"title\">config</span>-<span class=\"title\">china</span> --<span class=\"title\">registry</span>=<span class=\"title\">http</span>://<span class=\"title\">registry.npm.taobao.org</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"> </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">F</span>:\\<span class=\"title\">mywebsite</span>\\<span class=\"title\">blog</span>\\<span class=\"title\">thswind</span>&gt;<span class=\"title\">npm</span> <span class=\"title\">install</span> <span class=\"title\">node</span>-<span class=\"title\">sass</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"reference:\"><em>Reference:</em><a title=\"#reference:\" href=\"#reference:\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.fangr.cc/2017/09/27/hexo-workflow.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fangr.cc/2017/09/27/hexo-workflow.html</a></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"notes:\">Notes:<a title=\"#notes:\" href=\"#notes:\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>Maybe because of different os, there will be many warning and error information in cmd console. If you haven’t found a failed, then you can ignore it, or deal with it according to the tips.</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"Inside theme+MathJax","link":"2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax"},"next":{"title":"hexo+GitHub pages deploy","link":"2020/01/14/hexo+github pages deploy"},"plink":"http://thswind.github.io/2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages/","toc":[{"id":"1-install-node.js","title":"1 Install node.js","index":"1"},{"id":"2-install-git","title":"2 Install Git","index":"2"},{"id":"3-install-hexo","title":"3 Install hexo","index":"3"},{"id":"4-migration","title":"4 Migration","index":"4"},{"id":"problems","title":"Problems","index":"5","children":[{"id":"reference:","title":"Reference:","index":"5.1"}]},{"id":"notes:","title":"Notes:","index":"6"}],"reading_time":"358 words in 2 min"}